word_mean_info__list.difference: 指把某些东西压在一起或使占有较小空间。
普通用词，指一个物体在另一个物体上加压力。
多指从两面或多面施加压力来压紧、压碎或压出水来。
指某物受力被压偏或压碎。也指塞挤。
专指四面八方都压紧或塞满。

bilingual.source: I'd like to squeeze it and squeeze it till everybody had an equal share.
bilingual.target: 我想一直挤压它直到每个人都有平等的份额。

bilingual.source: I'd like to squeeze this round world into a new shape.
bilingual.target: 我想把这个圆圆的世界挤压成一个新形状。

bilingual.source: I'd like to squeeze this round world like a tube of toothpaste.
bilingual.target: 我想像挤牙膏一样挤压这个圆圆的世界。

bilingual.source: The child likes to squeeze the soft toy.
bilingual.target: 孩子喜欢挤压那个软玩具。

bilingual.source: He used force to squeeze the orange for juice.
bilingual.target: 他用力挤压橙子来榨汁。

bilingual.source: He tried to squeeze through the narrow gap.
bilingual.target: 他试图挤压通过狭窄的缝隙。

bilingual.source: She gave his hand a gentle squeeze to comfort him.
bilingual.target: 她轻轻挤压他的手以安慰他。

bilingual.source: You need to squeeze this toy to make a sound.
bilingual.target: 你需要挤压这个玩具才能发出声音。

bilingual.source: She squeeze the lemon to get some fresh juice.
bilingual.target: 她挤压柠檬来获取一些新鲜的果汁。

bilingual.source: The doctor advised him not to squeeze the furuncle.
bilingual.target: 医生建议他不要挤压那个疖子。

list.abstract: 《squeeze》是2016年Fifth Harmony演唱的一首歌曲，收录于专辑《7/27 (Deluxe)》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Buzz, mind if I squeeze in next to you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 巴斯，你介意我挤在你旁边吗?

yingyinNormal.en: Squeeze your legs together and cover the baby's ears.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把你的双腿并拢，别让宝宝听见了。

yingyinNormal.en: We use Caleb's compression algorithm to squeeze it all in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们使用迦勒的压缩算法把它挤进去。

yingyinNormal.en: Squeeze in. That's it. Historic occasion. Everyone, smile.
yingyinNormal.zh: 挤一挤。这是历史性的时刻。大家一起，微笑。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. No. I mean, why would I mind if I squeeze... squeeze in next to you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，不，我是说，我怎么会介意挤... 挤在你... 旁边呢?

yingyinNormal.en: Now, Chloe must squeeze in with Peppa and George. Move up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在，克洛伊必须要跟佩奇还有乔治挤在一起。让开一点。

yingyinNormal.en: Can I squeeze by? Randy! Randy, thank goodness. I need you on my team.
yingyinNormal.zh: 借过一下，蓝道，谢天谢地，我需要你加入。

yingyinNormal.en: I knew it would be some sort of dinosaur thing. Squeeze it's tummy. Too scary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我就知道礼物是跟恐龙有关的东西。按一下他的肚子！这太吓人了！

yingyinNormal.en: Come on man. Listen so, are you gonna squeeze the perps shoes a little bit before he lawyers up?
yingyinNormal.zh: 得了吧你，那你会在那贼人的律师出现前，先从他身上挤出一些汁来吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Wait, what are you... I bet we can both fit in this bed if we really trying on squeeze in there. No, wait.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，你要干吗？我赌咱俩能挤得下，用力挤挤就行……不，等等。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, for the final touch, this is an eyelash curler. You just place it on your lashes and squeeze it closed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，最后一步，用这个睫毛夹放在你睫毛上，然后贴近眼皮轻轻夹。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, my turn. My turn. Aunt Phoebe. Yes. Oh baby. Oh you're so cute. Oh I could squeeze your little head. I won't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，轮到我了。菲比阿姨。宝贝，你好可爱，我可以捏碎你小小的头，我不会那么做的。

yingyinNormal.en: Did you see his face? Maybe if that fat lump had given this a squeeze, he'd have remembered to fall on his fat arse.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看见他的脸吗？那胖墩要是捏一下这球就会记得用屁股着地。

yingyinNormal.en: There you all are. Now, Belinda Bear must squeeze in, too. Good job. We're like sardines in a tin. Where's everyone gone? Surprise.
yingyinNormal.zh: 原来你们躲在这里。现在，小熊贝琳达也挤到里面去了。让让我。我们像挤在罐头里的沙丁鱼，大家都跑到那去了，我们在这。

yingyinNormal.en: And a vibrant jobs market gives us the opportunity to keep up this progress and begin to undo that decades-long middle-class squeeze.
yingyinNormal.zh: 充满活力的就业市场让我们有机会继续这一进程，不再对中产阶层进行已经持续几十年的压榨。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, I was going to try to squeeze in a little more mocking before lunch, but I can come back later when you don't have a high powered weapon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我本想在吃午饭前溜过来吐吐槽，但我想我还是识相点撤吧，免得被你的杀伤性武器给殃及了。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: About half of U.S. jobs are at high risk of being automated with the middle class disproportionately <highlight>squeezed</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国约有一半的工作面临自动化的高风险，中产阶级受到了不成比例的挤压。

examination_example.sentence: But successive governments have presided over selling green spaces, <highlight>squeezing</highlight> money from local authorities and declining attention on sport in education.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但历届政府都在出售绿地，压榨地方当局的资金，并减少对体育教育的关注。

examination_example.sentence: Fundamentally, the USPS is in a historic <highlight>squeeze</highlight> between technological change.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从根本上说，美国邮政处于一种历史性的挤压之中。

examination_example.sentence: These plants will be targeted not at Iowa farmers trying to <highlight>squeeze</highlight> more cash out of high-yield fields.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些工厂的目标将不是爱荷华州的农民，他们试图从高产农田中赚取更多的钱。

sense_info_list.en: a difficult situation caused by reduction in money, jobs, or others

examination_example.sentence: Another factor is the <highlight>squeeze</highlight> that conventional dairy farmers have felt.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 另一个因素是传统奶农所感受到的经济苦难。
